[[PZL M-28| PZL M-28 Skytruck]] }} The '''14th Airlift Squadron''' is a newly established airlift squadron of the [[Polish Air Force]]. The unit is stationed at the [[33rd Air Base]] in [[Powidz]] with the [[7th Tactical Squadron]]. The unit operates 5 newly purchased [[Lockheed C-130 Hercules]] transport aircraft, the last being accepted in formal ceremony on 22 August 2012. ==References== {{Reflist}} [[Category:Squadrons of the Polish Air Force]] {{PolishAirForce-stub}}
